{
  "stem": "7069.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I think, if it wasn't so harsh that you were not allowed to go anyplace, it is really a good recipe for many, many youth groups, if they would cut down on all these mall visitings, and movies, and this stuff, and that stuff.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "If they would start to get together with their friends in their houses and--",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It's sort of like a captive situation there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Exactly.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, first of all, I have to go back for a moment.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Even though we were not allowed to go places, I still did.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I went to soccer games.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I went to concerts.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I went to the movie theater.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I came home after curfew.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And, of course, my poor mother-- and in those days, I didn't see it that way-- my poor mother just went out of here mind because it was prohibited.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And here and there we found out that somebody was caught and never seen again, that did the same thing.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And so when I went out and she says, well, you're going to be home-- if it was, oh, you're going to be home before 9 o'clock.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I said, Mom, I don't think so.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Don't worry about me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I suppose every parent and every youngster goes through that.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "You know, Ma, don't worry.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "You know, I am not a baby anymore.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Nothing will happen to me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I'm going to watch out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And so then, a close friend of mine disappeared.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And I had an answer for that too.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "His name was Robert Shapiro, that time.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So he, he disappeared.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I said-- and my mother said, now, you see what happened to him?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I said, Mom, I know he's a nice guy, but he is kind of careless.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I am not that way.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
